---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About MushroomWise - Building Trust Through Education & Community"
  description="Learn about MushroomWise.org, our mission to educate and connect people through science-backed mushroom wellness, and the story behind our community-driven platform."
>
  <section class="bg-teal-700 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About MushroomWise</h1>
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl">
        We're building a community-driven platform that educates and connects people through the power of functional mushrooms, fostering trust and wellness through science-backed knowledge.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
            <p>
              MushroomWise was born from a vision to make mushroom wellness accessible, trustworthy, and community-driven. We recognized that while functional mushrooms offer incredible benefits, the information landscape was fragmented and often overwhelming.
            </p>
            <p>
              Our founder's journey began with a personal transformation through mushroom wellness, which led to a deep passion for sharing this knowledge in a way that's clear, science-backed, and accessible to everyone.
            </p>
            <p>
              Today, we're building more than just an educational platform – we're creating a community where people can learn, share experiences, and discover the transformative power of mushrooms together.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-200 h-96 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400">
          <div class="text-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
            <p>Founder's story image</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Our Core Values</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-amber-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Education First</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We provide digestible, science-backed content that demystifies functional mushrooms and empowers informed wellness choices.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-teal-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Community-Driven</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We foster connection through storytelling, shared experiences, and a supportive community that grows together.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Transparency</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We believe in clear, honest communication and building trust through transparent, research-backed information.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Our Mission</h2>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
          To empower people with science-backed knowledge about functional mushrooms, fostering a community that supports each other's wellness journey while building trust in the MushroomAlive brand.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-left">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What We Do</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Create accessible, science-backed educational content</li>
              <li>• Build a supportive community of mushroom enthusiasts</li>
              <li>• Offer premium courses and resources</li>
              <li>• Connect people with quality mushroom products</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Impact</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Demystifying mushroom wellness</li>
              <li>• Building trust in the mushroom industry</li>
              <li>• Creating meaningful connections</li>
              <li>• Supporting informed wellness choices</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-teal-700 text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Join Our Growing Community</h2>
      <p class="text-xl opacity-90 mb-8">
        Be part of a community that's transforming wellness through the power of functional mushrooms.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <Button href="/community" isPrimary={true} isLarge={true}>
          Join the Inner Circle
        </Button>
        <Button href="/learn" isLarge={true}>
          Start Learning
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
